  "remarks": "British passport number 720134834, issued on 27 Jun. 2012 (expires on 27 Jun. 2022). Recruiter for Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant, listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (QDe.115), in the Syrian Arab Republic, and a key figure in the the Al-Khanssaa brigade, a female ISIL brigade established in Al-Raqqa to enforce ISIL’s interpretation of Sharia law. Sex: female. Photo available for inclusion in the INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020.; Listing: Listed on 28 Sep. 2015 (amended on 24 Nov. 2020)",
